<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Confirm your new email address</title>
  <style>
    /* Copy the exact same inline CSS from password-reset.hbs here */
    body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .button { display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background-color: #000; color: #fff !important; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: 500; margin: 20px 0; }
    .footer { margin-top: 40px; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid #eee; font-size: 12px; color: #666; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h2>Confirm your new email address</h2>
  <p>Hi {{name}},</p>
  <p>You requested to change your email address. Click the button below to confirm this change:</p>
  <p><a href="{{confirmUrl}}" class="button">Confirm New Email</a></p>
  <p>This link will expire in {{expiryHours}} hours.</p>
  <p>If you did not request this change, you can safely ignore this email — nothing will be changed.</p>
  <div class="footer">
    <p>If you're having trouble clicking the button, copy and paste this URL into your browser:</p>
    <p>{{confirmUrl}}</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
